    "description": "<strong>Ravenwood</strong> is a rogue-like survival game with some RPG aspects, survive as long as you can. Grow stronger for every run and advance in the realms of Ravenwood.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/956c3f9748ba8cfc91b1906142973d0b.poster.avif?t=1771892666\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/956c3f9748ba8cfc91b1906142973d0b.webm?t=1771892666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/956c3f9748ba8cfc91b1906142973d0b.mp4?t=1771892666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLE THE REALMS</h2>As the heroic protector of Ravenwood, you'll explore a vast, enchanting worlds filled with mystical creatures, realms and ancient secrets. Armed with powerful magic, you'll vanquish the forces of darkness and face ever-evolving challenges. Experience dynamic gameplay as you harness the full power of ancient spells, farm for gold, and strengthen your hero through every victory and defeat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/503c0258f323c66033c866edc8e7eec3.poster.avif?t=1771892666\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/503c0258f323c66033c866edc8e7eec3.webm?t=1771892666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/503c0258f323c66033c866edc8e7eec3.mp4?t=1771892666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MYSTICAL POWERS</h2>As you gain experience and level up, you'll unlock the ability to upgrade your spells, enhancing their power and versatility. Experiment with different combinations and discover new ways to harness your magical abilities. With every playthrough, you'll encounter different challenges and opportunities, ensuring a fresh and unique experience each time you dive into the Realms.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/2cd710351a29fe9da8b4014e7f5e1651.poster.avif?t=1771892666\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/2cd710351a29fe9da8b4014e7f5e1651.webm?t=1771892666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346230/extras/2cd710351a29fe9da8b4014e7f5e1651.mp4?t=1771892666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MADE FOR REPLAYABILITY</h2>With replayability in mind, no two expeditions are ever the same. Before setting out on your next run, you can visit the village merchant. There, you can purchase powerful upgrades and unique items to bolster your hero's abilities. Strategize, enhance your skills, and prepare for the unknown as you dive back into the ever-evolving realms of Ravenwood. Will you rise to the challenge and uncover all the secrets hidden within? The choice is yours!",
